Title: 205: Contributing to the community as a Data Science Influencer
Description:
In this episode of the SuperDataScience Podcast, I chat with the Data Science Influencer and Data Science Author, Kate Strachnyi. You will hear about Kate's journey to becoming a data science influencer, know how she is massively contributing to the data science community, and get insights how to create a culture of data science within an organization.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at www.superdatascience.com/205
